blogEntry.title: No Summer of Lisp
blogEntry.body:
Sadly we weren't chosen as a mentoring organization for the Summer of Code, we did manage to get feedback about the items Google values and are confident that we'll be included next year.

The upcoming meeting will be the first one that is webcast live, no registration is required just go to http://bbb.brandorr.com at the meeting time.
blogEntry.author: heow
